doop task to inherit the PATH environment from the task tracker. A mapper specified with a relative pathname (e.g. grep) will be automatically picked up from /bin.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=dhruba","name":"dhruba","key":"dhruba","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=dhruba&avatarId=30636","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=dhruba&avatarId=30636","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=dhruba&avatarId=30636","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=dhruba&avatarId=30636"},"displayName":"dhruba borthakur","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Tijuana"},"created":"2006-10-13T04:28:30.000+0000","updated":"2006-10-13T04:28:30.000+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12348580/comment/12442208","id":"12442208","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=arkady","name":"arkady","key":"arkady","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"arkady borkovsky","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"body":"\n   [[ Old comment, sent by email on Mon, 28 Aug 2006 22:55:04 -0700 ]]\n\nThanks, Owen!\n\nthis will remove some pain.\n\nPython example is not perfect though:  the version on the cluster is  \ndifferent from the version on lab machine.  On a local machine the  \ndefault is 2.4, while on the cluster it is 2.3.\n\n-- ab\n\n\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=arkady","name":"arkady","key":"arkady","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"arkady borkovsky","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"created":"2006-10-14T02:46:00.000+0000","updated":"2006-10-14T02:46:00.000+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12348580/comment/12442715","id":"12442715","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cutting","name":"cutting","key":"cutting","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Doug Cutting","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"I just committed this.  Thanks, Dhruba!","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cutting","name":"cutting","key":"cutting","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Doug Cutting","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2006-10-16T21:47:18.000+0000","updated":"2006-10-16T21:47:18.000+0000"}],"maxResults":8,"total":8,"startAt":0},"votes":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/HADOOP-477/votes","votes":0,"hasVoted":false},"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":0,"worklogs":[]},"customfield_12311820":"0|i0ioav:"}}